profile:
Luxia as the name suggests is luxury. Luxury is timeless. The experience and the history that Luxia brings to all its clients is timeless quality.

Luxia has over 20 years knowledge of in-house manufacturing quality cabinetry. Our mission is to make clients’ visions come true utilizing our design skills, innovative up-to-date designs, current products/materials, and expert installations.

Our commitment to our clients is unsurpassed and no project is insurmountable.

Luxia Kitchens continually invests in state-of-the-art technology, maintaining its leading edge and constantly strives to achieve excellence.

Luxia values its long-term relationships with employees, suppliers, and customers.
products:
Custom kitchens

Custom Closets
services:
Consultation & custom designing with 3D software as per Clients requirement.
Production of customized cabinets.
Installation.
Complete Mill work.

profile: The Laundry Lift provides outdoor and indoor laundry drying products. Greenway® is committed to engineering and developing products that are energy efficient and environmentally friendly. As an extension of our current offerings we are proud to introduce a new line of Greenway® Laundry Drying Solutions. Clothes dryers rank as one of the highest energy consumption items in homes today. With this in mind, our laundry products offer a strong eco-friendly benefit along with significant cost savings on energy bills. Additionally, line drying is less damaging to fabrics resulting in longer lasting garments.
